name: Palmeti Silk WallcoveringLuminosa – Single Roll(33in X 15ft)
description: Shanan Campanaro looked to her parents’ Tuscan style garden in Southern California in painting the source artwork for Palmeti, a 100% silk wallpaper pattern reminiscent of palms blowing in the wind. Gestural curves and subtle brushstrokes capture the movement of these trees perfectly, lending a sense of natural freedom to your environment. The Luminosa colorway presents peachy pink tones. This pattern is also available on our classic clay-coated paper.

name: Aquarelle WallpaperOcean – Single Roll(27" X 15ft)
description: Kassia x Eskayel Aquarelle luxury wallpapers pay tribute to the power and unique aesthetic of water. Using fluid lines inspired by a birds-eye view of rivers spilling into the sea, the Ocean colorway features a rich palette of blues. As a custom wallpaper, Aquarelle comes in a choice of three colorways. Celebrate the deep beauty of dynamic bodies of water with Kassia x Eskayel Aquarelle wallpaper in Ocean.

name: Clemente WallpaperSol – Single Roll(27" X 15ft)
description: With references including a French Art Deco rug, the Cabrillo Bridge in downtown San Diego, eucalyptus trees, and a Gauguin painting that hung on the wall of her school, Eskayel's Shanan Campanaro drew on her suburban upbringing in Southern California in the 1980s and 1990s to create the Presidio Collection. Her Clemente design depicts abstracted trees with voluminous foliage. It is available to order as high-end custom wallpaper, luxury fabric, and pillows with feather inserts in several colorways. Sol provides a palette of greys with tan and pink.

name: Galileo Glass WallpaperIndigo – Single Roll(27" X 15ft)
description: Fluid pigments create symmetrical abstract patterns that explore both movement and stillness. Inspired by a trip to Tuscany, Galileo is a rich, saturated design that draws the eye and invites exploration. In the Indigo colorway, expect shades of deep blue. This pattern is available as luxurious high-end wallpaper.

name: Travelers Palm WallpaperDusk – Single Roll(27" X 15ft)
description: With expansive leaves that mimic a fan, a majestic tree in Mexico inspired the Travelers Palm pattern from our Ecuatorial Geometry collection. Watercolor representations of this giant tropical plant are repeated against a geometric background of overlapping scallops. In our Dusk colorway, the palette is mainly green and beige. Travelers Palm wallpaper is available to order with a luxurious clay coated finish.

name: Prospect Silk WallcoveringVerde – Single Roll(33in Wide,
description: Designed to lift the mood like a spell spent in nature, the 100% silk Prospect wallpaper mural represents the experience of being immersed in foliage, ascending through the trees, and eventually arriving at the ethereal sky. Prospect can be used on its own or in tandem with the companion design Stratus, a wallpaper that uses the same pattern repeat as the sky found along Prospect’s upper dimension. Use Stratus to extend the height of the Prospect mural and even wrap your ceiling. This pattern is also available on our classic clay-coated paper.For the full color story of this design, order 8” x 10” samples in both Prospect and Stratus. The Prospect sample shows the leaf detail, while the Stratus sample shows the sky detail.

name: Stratus Silk WallcoveringSky – Single Roll(33in X 15ft)
description: Based on a peaceful nature walk through the parks, streets, and lush community gardens of Brooklyn, Eskayel’s 100% silk Stratus wallpaper is a gentle tribute to the skies above. The repeating pattern in Sky offers a light-as-air quality through a pale blue palette. Stratus can be used on its own or in tandem with the companion design Prospect, a mural that incorporates the same pattern repeat along its upper dimension. Use Stratus to extend the height of the Prospect mural and even wrap a ceiling. This pattern is also available on our classic clay-coated paper.

name: Empyrean Silk MuralDawn – Single Roll(33in Wide,
description: Shanan Campanaro created the Eskayel design Empyrean after exploring the Maldivian atolls by boat. Inspired by the endless skies and sunsets, she painted a large mural collage in watercolor to serve as the source artwork for the pattern. Printed on our delicate 100% silk backed with paper and classic clay-coated paper, Empyrean wallpaper in Dawn offers a multicolor palette.

name: Empyrean Wallpaper MuralCyrrus – Single Roll(27in Wide,
description: Eskayel creative director Shanan Campanaro is the artist behind luxurious Empyrean, a dreamy design inspired by a spell living at sea among the Maldivian atolls. Inspired by endless skyscapes and sunsets, a large mural collage in watercolor provided the source artwork for the pattern. Available to order in the navy Cyrrus colorway on our classic clay-coated paper and 100% silk backed with paper.

name: Empyrean Silk MuralDusk – Single Roll(33in Wide,
description: Shanan Campanaro created the Eskayel pattern Empyrean following an extended boat trip to explore the Maldivian. To capture the endless skies and sunsets, she painted a large mural collage in watercolor. This served as the source artwork for the pattern. Printed on our delicate 100% silk backed with paper and classic clay-coated paper, Empyrean wallpaper in Dusk provides a multicolor palette.

name: Empyrean Wallpaper MuralAir – Single Roll(27in Wide,
description: A dreamy design inspired by scenes from exotic locations, Empyrean began when Shanan Campanaro spent a spell living at sea among the Maldivian atolls. The limitless skies and their otherworldly sunsets stuck in her mind, eventually spilling out as a large mural collage painted in watercolor. Air is a colorway of purple and blue. It is available on our classic clay-coated paper and 100% silk backed with paper.

name: Shoal Silk WallcoveringCay – Single Roll(33in X 15ft)
description: In a vision of tropical fish suspended in their aquatic habitat, Shoal was inspired by an afternoon of underwater swimming in the Maldives. Shanan Campanaro captured the design in watercolor from memory, lending it a dreamlike feel and a unique quality of stillness. In the Cay colorway, this 100% silk backed with paper provides a palette of purple hues. This pattern is also available on our classic clay-coated paper.

name: Shoal Silk WallcoveringOcean – Single Roll(33in X 15ft)
description: In a composition painted from memory, Shanan Campanaro created the Shoal pattern following an otherworldly experience while snorkeling around the Maldivian atolls. The design – which depicts tropical fish in profile in their aquatic environment – captures the silent stillness of swimming beneath the surface. In the Ocean colorway, 100% silk backed with paper introduces a blue palette to an interior scheme. This pattern is also available on our classic clay-coated paper.

name: Shoal Silk WallcoveringShell – Single Roll(33in X 15ft)
description: Based on a memory of snorkeling in the warm waters of the Maldives, Shanan Campanaro’s Shoal design captures her otherworldly encounters with marine life. The composition features tropical fish in profile suspended in their natural environment. Reimagining the peaceful silence of diving down beneath the water’s surface, luxurious 100% silk wallpaper in the Shell colorway lends beige tones to interior schemes.  This pattern is also available on our classic clay-coated paper.

name: Shoal WallpaperCoral – Single Roll(27" X 15ft)
description: Working from memory, Shanan Campanaro painted the Shoal pattern after an inspiring snorkeling session in the atolls of the Maldives. The scene represents a school of tropical fish floating in their liquid environment. Capturing the stillness of being held up by warm water, this classic clay-coated wallpaper in the Coral colorway presents a palette of red shades. This pattern is also available on our 100% silk backed with paper.

name: Atoll Silk WallcoveringAmber – Single Roll(33in X 15ft)
description: Inspired by a snorkel session through the fish, seaweed, shells, and coral of the Maldives, Atoll is a fluid wallpaper design that gazes into the watery world of ocean creatures. With its dreamlike, moody feel, Atoll comes in a choice of six tranquil colorways in luxurious 100% silk backed with paper and our classic clay-coated wallpaper. Amber provides a palette of brown shades.

name: Atoll Silk WallcoveringReef – Single Roll(33in X 15ft)
description: Memories of an awe-inducing snorkeling excursion in the Maldives among fish, seaweed, coral, and other ocean creatures prompted Shanan Campanaro to create the source artwork for Atoll. The fluid, dreamlike design captures her view of this hidden underwater world. Atoll is printed to order in six tranquil colorways on our 100% silk backed with paper and classic clay-coated paper. The Reef palette presents a background of green.

name: Atoll Silk WallcoveringCoral – Single Roll(33in X 15ft)
description: Following a snorkeling excursion with fish, seaweed, coral, and other ocean life of the Maldives, Shanan Campanaro painted the source artwork for Atoll silk wallcoverings from fleeting memories. The watery design captures this secret aquatic world. As a dreamlike backdrop, Atoll is printed to order in six tranquil colorways. The Coral palette offers a range of red hues. This pattern is also available on our classic clay-coated paper.

name: Atoll WallpaperOcean – Single Roll(27" X 15ft)
description: Following an awe-inducing snorkeling excursion in the Maldives among fish, seaweed, coral, and other ocean creatures, Shanan Campanaro painted the source artwork for Atoll from memory. The watery, dreamlike design captures her vision of this hidden aquatic world. This pattern is printed to order in six tranquil colorways on our classic clay-coated paper and 100% silk backed with paper. The Ocean palette offers a blue background.

name: Swim WallpaperLake – Single Roll(27" X 15ft)
description: A fun composition that celebrates the sweet sensation of water on the skin, Swim is a playful luxury wallpaper. In the Lake colorway, waterborne figures appear against a navy blue background. A strong choice for beach houses and powder rooms.
